rComments: Explains all the concepts clearly and super neat handwritings. He is also really patient with students asking questions. The materials itself is pretty hard though.
Highly recommend taking is class. Super clear and detailed lectures and is really helpful in office hours. Just sit near the front, cause his writing is small!
patient and super nice, I really enjoy his class!!

The prof was super nice! If you don't understand something you can always go up to the prof and ask. I went once and he did help :)  But tbh, I didn't come to class that often and still ended up getting an 80. You'll do fine just by looking at the textbook and past tests because the lecture content was nothing compared to the actual tests.
